**Query #5**

    -- 5: Days Between Orders (MySQL Version)
    SELECT 
        customer_id, 
        order_date, 
        DATEDIFF(
            order_date, 
            LAG(order_date) OVER (
                PARTITION BY customer_id 
                ORDER BY order_date
            )
        ) AS days_gap
    FROM sales;

